{
  "stem": "12255.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know that there were many very old women, but more in the 50s downwards.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And not too many very young children, mostly teenagers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Were sent away, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There, we had no trouble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were eager to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They saw the place, and they-- they were eager to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't-- it-- it was only a mile, a mile and a quarter away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember how we got them there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- many of them might have walked, even.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so there was little trouble there, over that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Must have been about three or four weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, it was burnt down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite amusing, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was ceremonially-- all the brigadiers and the-- and all the big shots came, and they brought flame throwers and-- to burn it down.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the first two shots missed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Eventually, they managed to get it ignited, and it was burned to the ground.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing was left.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
